==========================================
Modification history of stoichcalc package
==========================================


Changes from 1.1-4 to 1.1-5:
----------------------------

- updated email address


Changes from 1.1-3 to 1.1-4:
----------------------------

- matching line length limit in Rd files


Changes from 1.1-2 to 1.1-3:
----------------------------

- Argument "verbose" added to "calc.stoich.basis" and "calc.stoich.coef"

- NAMESPACE added


Changes from 1.1-1 to 1.1-2:
----------------------------

- Citations directly on help pages / reference updated

- New version number (in DESCRIPTION and stoichcalc.Rd) 1.1-2

- New file /inst/CITATION

- In help files "library" replaced by "package"


Changes from 1.1-0 to 1.1-1:
----------------------------

- Spelling in reference corrected to Schuwirth

- Charge of NO3- corrected in examples

- Analysis of structure of stoichiometric space added


